    <statement><p>Multiply the polynomials.</p>
<p><m>\left({5r-4}\right)\left({r+2}\right)=</m><fillin characters="32" name="AnSwEr0001"/></p>
</statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>5r^{2}+6r-8</m>
      </p>
    </answer>
    <solution><p>We use the FOIL technique: <alert>F</alert>irst <alert>O</alert>utside <alert>I</alert>nside <alert>L</alert>ast. <me>\begin{aligned}
              \left({5r-4}\right)({r+2})\amp ={5r^{2}+10r-4r-8}\\
                                \amp ={5r^{2}+6r-8}
      \end{aligned}</me></p>
</solution>
